All background images should be scaled to 1920x1080

To add your CyberKid:
- First download the original image from IPFS
- Then remove the background color leaving a transparent background
(use photoshop etc) and save as transparent PNG (1000x1000).

*CyberKids cannot be updated more than once. F5 to refresh.*
